BlackBerry Cylance: Results
MITRE Engenuity does not assign scores, rankings, or ratings. The evaluation results are available to the public, so other organizations may provide their own analysis and interpretation - these are not endorsed or validated by MITRE.

Alerting Strategy

The CylanceOPTICS detection's view contains all the enriched information about what potentially malicious activity took place. Each alert has a descriptive title and description with potential mapping(s) to related ATT&CK Tactics and Techniques. The detection logic is shown in-line along with the system events that lead to the alert. Alert severity is listed as informational, low, medium, and high.

Correlation Strategy

Alerts are aggregated by host and can be sorted by chronological order in the CylanceOPTICS detection view. Additional correlation happens in CylanceOPTICS Focus Data view which shows process lineage and each action that occurred in a given process tree over time.
